author: Nintendo of America
description:
Spray your worries away in PowerWash Simulator 2, out now on Nintendo Switch 2: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/powerwash-simulator-2-switch-2/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=P1021-01&utm_id=P1021-01  

Play through a fresh new campaign and venture even further to new locations to complete jobs. Reach new heights of power-washing professionalism with a new range of tools to achieve that sparkle, high and low. Take a breather at your home base and make it your own with your collection of trinkets and furniture. And don't worry, no pets left behind as your pretty kitties are along for the ride.

author: Nintendo of America
description:
Hyrule Warriors: Age of Imprisonment launches Nov 6, 2025, exclusively on Nintendo Switch 2. Pre-order now: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/hyrule-warriors-age-of-imprisonment-switch-2/?utm_source=SW-AA&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=S1012-01&utm_id=S1012-01 
 
Darkness stirs as Ganondorf's shadow spreads across Hyrule. As the Imprisoning War unfolds, the stakes are higher than ever. Rulers, Rauru and Sonia—alongside the Sages—must unite their people to face the growing threat. Along the way, new allies emerge and together, they must defend their kingdom and drive back the darkness threatening to consume it.
